{"id":150875,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/ipad2登陸-搶買互毆4傷/","date":"2011-05-08T19:00:57Z","modified":"2011-05-08T19:00:57Z","title":"iPad2登陸 搶買互毆4傷","content":"<p><a href=\"http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33372889/IssueID/20110508/pvtype/r\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20110508/33372889_5657066da6dec2a9586131f23cfedcf1_120x120.jpg\" /></a><br />【大陸中心╱綜合外電報導】蘋果第二代平板電腦iPad2前天上午在中國開賣，包括北京、上海等地的蘋果電腦直營店外，前一天起即分別湧入上千名「果粉」（蘋果電腦粉絲）聚集守候。北京三里屯的蘋果店外，昨更爆發搶購民眾衝突，其間有人互毆、撞碎一道玻璃門，最少4人受傷，導致該蘋果專賣店暫停營業。 </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33372889/IssueID/20110508/pvtype/r\">詳全文：iPad2登陸 搶買互毆4傷</a><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://rss.feedsportal.com/c/33277/f/585303/s/14ab56e6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=iPad2%E7%99%BB%E9%99%B8+%E6%90%B6%E8%B2%B7%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%864%E5%82%B7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.nextmedia.com%2Fapplenews%2Farticle%2Fart_id%2F33372889%2FIssueID%2F20110508%2Fpvtype%2Fr\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=iPad2%E7%99%BB%E9%99%B8+%E6%90%B6%E8%B2%B7%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%864%E5%82%B7&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.nextmedia.com%2Fapplenews%2Farticle%2Fart_id%2F33372889%2FIssueID%2F20110508%2Fpvtype%2Fr\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091572775/u/0/f/585303/c/33277/s/14ab56e6/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091572775/u/0/f/585303/c/33277/s/14ab56e6/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20110508/33372889_5657066da6dec2a9586131f23cfedcf1_120x120.jpg\" /></